Cinerate by Emavisuals.

Cinerate is an app created by emavisuals. This SERVICE is provided by emavisuals at no cost and is intended for use as is. The app does not include ads,
but they might be implemented in future updates of the app. 


** Information Collection and Use **
The app can be used freely without creating a user account, with limited services. In order to use the full functionalities of the app,
there is the possiblity to create an account. When creating a new account, the following information are required: an email, an username, and a password.
The email is not visible by other users, whereas the username is VISIBLE BY ANYONE. Do not add your full name, it is not required.
These information are store on Google Cloud Firestore database. 

This information is stored only on your phone and on cloud firestore. I do not share them with other third parties. 

If you wish to know which information is stored about you, and if you want to completely delete them from Cloud Firestore,
send an email to emavisuals@gmail.com




** Links to Other Sites **

This Service contains links to other sites. 
By clicking on the 'info' section, you click on a third-party link, and you will be directed to that site. 
Other third-party links may be used within the app.
Note that these external sites are not operated by me. 
Therefore, I strongly advise you to review the Privacy Policy of these websites. 
I have no control over and assume no responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party sites or services.


** Childrenâ€™s Privacy **

